msgid ""
"Understand Klein for Ray graph contexts, sinks, execution handles, job "
"states, identifiers, cancellation, failures, resource plans, and cleanup."
msgstr "了解 Klein for Ray 的图上下文、接收器、执行句柄、作业状态、标识符、取消、故障、资源计划和清理。"

msgid "Job lifecycle"
msgstr "作业生命周期"

msgid "A Klein job has two distinct lifetimes:"
msgstr "Klein 作业有两个不同的生命周期："

msgid ""
"On the driver, module-level APIs build a lazy graph ending in one or more"
" sinks; an internal pipeline owner keeps their shared state."
msgstr "在驱动程序上，模块级 API 构建一个以一个或多个接收器结尾的惰性图；内部管道所有者保存它们的共享状态。"

msgid ""
"`execute()` compiles that graph and either runs a Ray Data batch job to "
"completion or submits a native streaming job to a detached `JobManager`."
msgstr "`execute()` 编译该图，然后运行 Ray Data 批处理作业直至完成，或向分离式 `JobManager` 提交原生流处理作业。"

msgid ""
"Keeping the builder, submitted job, and returned handle separate makes "
"deployment and cleanup predictable. This page describes those boundaries."
msgstr "将构建器、已提交作业和返回的句柄彼此分离，可使部署与清理变得可预测。本页说明这些边界。"

msgid "Build one graph, then execute it"
msgstr "构建一个图，然后执行"

msgid ""
"Streams created together share graph configuration, identifiers, and SQL "
"session state. Streams from different isolated pipelines cannot be "
"combined."
msgstr "一起创建的流共享图配置、标识符和 SQL 会话状态。来自不同隔离管道的流不能组合。"

msgid "The normal API keeps that owner out of application code:"
msgstr "常规 API 不会将该所有者暴露给应用代码："

msgid "Advanced isolation"
msgstr "高级隔离"

msgid ""
"Create an explicit context only when one process must build independent "
"pipelines or needs isolated configuration:"
msgstr "仅当一个进程必须构建多个独立管道或需要隔离配置时，才创建显式上下文："

msgid ""
"Creating a terminal operation such as `show()`, `take_all()`, or "
"`write_*()` constructs a `StreamSink` and immediately registers it with "
"that context. The graph remains lazy: registration does not read records "
"or create workers."
msgstr ""
"创建 `show()`、`take_all()` 或 `write_*()` 等终端操作时，会构造一个 `StreamSink` "
"并立即将其注册到该上下文。图仍是惰性的：注册不会读取记录，也不会创建工作节点。"

msgid ""
"`execute(\"job-name\")` uses every terminal currently registered in the "
"pipeline. A successful submission consumes those registrations; an "
"exception keeps them available for inspection or retry. A retry can "
"repeat side effects that completed before a batch failure, so connector "
"delivery guarantees still apply. Register all branches first, then call "
"`execute()` once to submit them as one job. Use a fresh `KleinContext` "
"only for an independently configured logical job."
msgstr ""
"`execute(\"job-name\")` "
"会使用管道中当前注册的每个终端。提交成功后会消费这些注册；发生异常时则会保留它们，以供检查或重试。重试可能重复批处理失败前已经完成的副作用，因此连接器的交付保证仍然适用。请先注册所有分支，再调用一次"
" `execute()`，将它们作为一个作业提交。仅为配置相互独立的逻辑作业使用新的 `KleinContext`。"

msgid ""
"`reset_context()` remains a deprecated compatibility helper for ambient "
"module-level pipelines. New module-level code should finish graph "
"construction with terminal operations and call `execute(\"job-name\")`; "
"use an explicit context only for the advanced isolation case."
msgstr ""
"`reset_context()` 仍是面向环境式模块级管道的已弃用兼容辅助函数。新的模块级代码应通过终端操作完成图构建，然后调用 "
"`execute(\"job-name\")`；仅在高级隔离场景中使用显式上下文。"

msgid "Explain before execution"
msgstr "执行前查看计划"

msgid ""
"`explain()` compiles the registered graph and returns its resource plan "
"as JSON. It does not initialize Ray, create a `JobManager`, run a source,"
" or invoke a sink:"
msgstr "`explain()` 编译已注册的图，并以 JSON 返回其资源计划。它不会初始化 Ray、创建 `JobManager`、运行源或调用接收器："

msgid ""
"Attach every intended sink before calling `explain`; the plan includes "
"every terminal currently registered in that pipeline. Explaining does not"
" consume the registrations, so the following `execute(\"multiply-ids\")` "
"submits the same graph as long as no other terminals are added in "
"between."
msgstr ""
"调用 `explain` "
"之前，请附加所有预期接收器；计划会包含该管道中当前注册的每个终端。查看计划不会消费这些注册，因此只要期间没有再添加其他终端，随后调用 "
"`execute(\"multiply-ids\")` 就会提交同一个图。"

msgid ""
"Plan construction includes the Ray Serve graph rewrite and any resource "
"plan loaded through the environment. It can also persist the resulting "
"resource plan when requested. Operator chaining and physical streaming "
"expansion happen later during submission, so use the runtime "
"observability view for the final physical task set."
msgstr ""
"计划构建包括 Ray Serve "
"图重写以及通过环境加载的任何资源计划；按要求还可以持久化所得资源计划。算子链化和物理流处理展开会在稍后的提交阶段发生，因此最终物理任务集应以运行时可观测性视图为准。"

msgid "Execute a job"
msgstr "执行作业"

msgid ""
"At least one sink is required. Without one, `execute()` raises a "
"`ValueError` instead of running an unconsumed stream. Pass a stable name "
"to production jobs; calling `execute()` without one creates a random "
"display name."
msgstr ""
"至少需要一个接收器。若没有接收器，`execute()` 会抛出 "
"`ValueError`，而不是运行无人消费的流。请为生产作业传入稳定的名称；不带名称调用 `execute()` 会创建随机显示名称。"

msgid "Execution has three possible paths:"
msgstr "执行有三条可能的路径："

msgid "Path"
msgstr "路径"

msgid "What `execute()` does"
msgstr "`execute()` 执行的操作"

msgid "Returned handle"
msgstr "返回的句柄"

msgid "Batch"
msgstr "批处理"

msgid ""
"Compiles the graph to Ray Data, executes every sink synchronously, and "
"returns after completion."
msgstr "将图编译到 Ray Data，同步执行每个接收器，并在完成后返回。"

msgid "`CompletedJobHandle`"
msgstr "`CompletedJobHandle`"

msgid "Native streaming"
msgstr "原生流处理"

msgid ""
"Initializes Ray if necessary, creates and schedules a detached job, and "
"returns after submission succeeds."
msgstr "必要时初始化 Ray，创建并调度分离式作业，并在提交成功后返回。"

msgid "`LiveJobHandle`"
msgstr "`LiveJobHandle`"

msgid "Compile-only"
msgstr "仅编译"

msgid "Builds the logical graph but runs no source, UDF, or sink."
msgstr "构建逻辑图，但不运行任何源、UDF 或接收器。"

msgid ""
"In `execution.runtime.mode=auto`, an unbounded source, any graph vertex "
"without a batch lowering, or `udf.ignore-exception=true` selects "
"streaming. Only a bounded graph whose every vertex can lower to Ray Data "
"and whose record-level ignore-exception policy is disabled selects batch."
" This check includes sources, intermediate transformations, and sinks, so"
" a bounded custom source or a graph containing streaming-only `key_by`, "
"managed state, `map_reduce`, windows, or joins selects streaming "
"automatically. A production deployment can still pin `streaming` "
"deliberately when mode changes should require a configuration review."
msgstr ""
"在 `execution.runtime.mode=auto` 模式下，存在无界数据源、任一计算图顶点没有批处理下沉实现，或设置 "
"`udf.ignore-exception=true`，都会选择原生流处理。只有计算图有界、每个顶点都能下沉到 Ray Data，且记录级忽略异常策略已禁用时，才会选择批处理。此检查涵盖数据源、中间转换和 "
"sink，因此，即使自定义数据源有界，或者图中包含仅支持流处理的 `key_by`、托管状态、`map_reduce`、窗口或连接，也会自动选择流处理。若模式变更应经过配置审查，生产部署仍可有意固定为 "
"`streaming`。"

msgid ""
"Conversely, selecting streaming cannot make a Ray Data-only source or "
"operation streamable. Check [operator compatibility](operator-"
"compatibility.md) whenever the graph mixes execution families."
msgstr ""
"反过来，选择流处理也无法让仅支持 Ray Data 的源或操作变得可流式执行。只要图中混用了不同执行系列，就请检查[算子兼容性"
"](operator-compatibility.md)。"

msgid ""
"Batch execution and initial streaming submission can fail before a handle"
" is returned. Those exceptions are raised directly from `execute()`. A "
"live handle reports failures that occur after successful submission."
msgstr "批处理执行和初始流处理提交可能在返回句柄之前失败。这些异常会直接从 `execute()` 抛出。实时句柄报告成功提交之后发生的故障。"

msgid "Use the returned handle"
msgstr "使用返回的句柄"

msgid "The two handle types intentionally have different meanings:"
msgstr "两种句柄类型有意采用不同的含义："

msgid "Operation"
msgstr "操作"

msgid "`status`"
msgstr "`status`"

msgid "Always `JobStatus.FINISHED`."
msgstr "始终为 `JobStatus.FINISHED`。"

msgid "RPC to the job's `JobManager`."
msgstr "对作业 `JobManager` 的 RPC。"

msgid "`wait()`"
msgstr "`wait()`"

msgid "Returns immediately."
msgstr "立即返回。"

msgid ""
"Blocks without polling until a terminal state; raises `KleinError` for "
"`FAILED`."
msgstr "不轮询地阻塞到终态；对于 `FAILED` 抛出 `KleinError`。"

msgid "`get()`"
msgstr "`get()`"

msgid "Returns the in-memory batch result or compile-only logical graph."
msgstr "返回内存中的批处理结果或仅编译逻辑图。"

msgid "Waits for terminal state and drains one collecting sink's output queue."
msgstr "等待终态并排空一个收集型接收器的输出队列。"

msgid "`cancel(timeout=60)`"
msgstr "`cancel(timeout=60)`"

msgid "Returns `True`; there is no live work to stop."
msgstr "返回 `True`；没有需要停止的实时工作。"

msgid "Requests coordinated teardown and returns whether cancellation completed."
msgstr "请求协调式拆除，并返回取消是否完成。"

msgid "`namespace`"
msgstr "`namespace`"

msgid "`None`."
msgstr "`None`。"

msgid "The Ray namespace/job identifier."
msgstr "Ray 命名空间/作业标识符。"

msgid ""
"Use `get()` only when the job contains one result-producing terminal. "
"Klein enforces that `take()` or `take_all()` is the job's only terminal "
"in both batch and streaming modes, so collection has one consistent "
"contract. Use `wait()` for one or more side-effect terminals. Batch "
"errors have already been raised by `execute()`, before the completed "
"handle exists."
msgstr ""
"仅当作业包含一个产生结果的终端时才使用 `get()`。无论批处理还是流处理模式，Klein 都会强制要求 `take()` 或 "
"`take_all()` 是作业的唯一终端，从而让收集具有一致的契约。对于一个或多个产生副作用的终端，请使用 `wait()`。批处理错误早已由 "
"`execute()` 在完成句柄存在之前抛出。"

msgid ""
"Use `wait()` for ordinary streaming sink jobs. `LiveJobHandle.get()` is a"
" special collection boundary: the graph must contain exactly one "
"collecting operator such as `take()` or `take_all()`. It is not a general"
" way to retrieve file, Kafka, SQL, or custom sink results. It also drains"
" after terminal status without performing `wait()`'s explicit failed-"
"status check, so use `wait()` or check `status` when failure propagation "
"matters."
msgstr ""
"普通流处理接收器作业应使用 `wait()`。`LiveJobHandle.get()` 是一个特殊的收集边界：图必须恰好包含一个收集算子，例如 "
"`take()` 或 `take_all()`。它不是获取文件、Kafka、SQL 或自定义接收器结果的通用方式。它还会在终态后排空队列，而不执行"
" `wait()` 的显式失败状态检查，因此当故障传播很重要时，请使用 `wait()` 或检查 `status`。"

msgid ""
"If `LiveJobHandle.wait()` receives `KeyboardInterrupt` or `SystemExit`, "
"it attempts a five-second cancellation and then re-raises the signal "
"exception. Simply allowing the submitting process to exit without waiting"
" is different: the detached streaming job continues on the Ray cluster."
msgstr ""
"如果 `LiveJobHandle.wait()` 收到 `KeyboardInterrupt` 或 "
"`SystemExit`，它会尝试在五秒内取消作业，然后重新抛出信号异常。仅让提交进程退出而不等待则不同：分离式流处理作业会继续在 Ray "
"集群上运行。"

msgid "Job states"
msgstr "作业状态"

msgid "`JobStatus` defines five non-terminal and three terminal states:"
msgstr "`JobStatus` 定义了五个非终态和三个终态："

msgid "State"
msgstr "状态"

msgid "Terminal"
msgstr "是否终态"

msgid "Meaning"
msgstr "含义"

msgid "`CREATED`"
msgstr "`CREATED`"

msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

msgid "The `JobManager` exists but has not accepted a graph."
msgstr "`JobManager` 已存在，但尚未接受图。"

msgid "`SUBMITTING`"
msgstr "`SUBMITTING`"

msgid "The graph is being optimized, expanded, restored, and scheduled."
msgstr "正在优化、展开、恢复和调度图。"

msgid "`DEPLOYING`"
msgstr "`DEPLOYING`"

msgid "A valid public lifecycle state reserved for deployment progress."
msgstr "为部署进度预留的有效公共生命周期状态。"

msgid "`INITIALIZING`"
msgstr "`INITIALIZING`"

msgid "A valid public lifecycle state reserved for task initialization progress."
msgstr "为任务初始化进度预留的有效公共生命周期状态。"

msgid "`RUNNING`"
msgstr "`RUNNING`"

msgid "Submission succeeded and supervision is active."
msgstr "提交成功且监督处于活动状态。"

msgid "`FINISHED`"
msgstr "`FINISHED`"

msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

msgid "All tasks reached normal completion and teardown ran."
msgstr "所有任务均正常完成，并且已执行拆除。"

msgid "`CANCELLED`"
msgstr "`CANCELLED`"

msgid "User cancellation completed teardown."
msgstr "用户取消已完成拆除。"

msgid "`FAILED`"
msgstr "`FAILED`"

msgid "Submission, recovery, or runtime supervision failed permanently."
msgstr "提交、恢复或运行时监督永久失败。"

msgid "The current streaming manager normally follows one of these paths:"
msgstr "当前流处理管理器通常遵循以下路径之一："

msgid ""
"`DEPLOYING` and `INITIALIZING` are part of the enum so clients must "
"tolerate them, but the current manager does not explicitly publish them "
"during normal submission. A successfully returned live handle is usually "
"already `RUNNING` because `execute()` waits for scheduling to succeed. "
"Status snapshots retain a timestamped transition history for diagnosis."
msgstr ""
"`DEPLOYING` 和 `INITIALIZING` "
"是枚举的一部分，因此客户端必须能够处理它们，但当前管理器在正常提交期间不会显式发布这两个状态。成功返回的实时句柄通常已经是 "
"`RUNNING`，因为 `execute()` 会等待调度成功。状态快照会保留带时间戳的转换历史以供诊断。"

msgid ""
"A finite source naturally propagates end-of-data through every sink; once"
" all tasks finish, the job becomes `FINISHED`. A bounded collecting "
"operation such as `take(n)` can request graceful source drain. Neither "
"case is cancellation."
msgstr ""
"有限源会自然地通过每个接收器传播数据结束信号；所有任务完成后，作业变为 `FINISHED`。`take(n)` "
"等有界收集操作可以请求优雅排空源。这两种情况都不属于取消。"

msgid "Job names, namespaces, and job IDs"
msgstr "作业名称、命名空间与作业 ID"

msgid ""
"`job_name` is the human-readable logical label used in logs, plans, "
"lineage, and metrics. A native streaming submission also gets a Ray "
"namespace. Without an explicit setting, its shape is:"
msgstr "`job_name` 是用于日志、计划、血缘和指标的可读逻辑标签。原生流处理提交还会获得一个 Ray 命名空间。未显式设置时，其形式为："

msgid ""
"The embedded name is lowercased, runs of non-alphanumeric characters "
"become a dash, and it is capped at 40 characters. The random suffix lets "
"two submissions with the same `job_name` coexist safely."
msgstr "嵌入的名称会转换为小写，连续的非字母数字字符会变为短横线，并限制为 40 个字符。随机后缀使具有相同 `job_name` 的两个提交能够安全共存。"

msgid ""
"Set `job.namespace` only when operations tooling needs a stable "
"identifier:"
msgstr "仅当运维工具需要稳定标识符时才设置 `job.namespace`："

msgid ""
"An explicit non-empty namespace is used verbatim. Do not reuse it while "
"an old detached job's named actors still exist."
msgstr "显式的非空命名空间会原样使用。旧分离式作业的具名 actor 仍存在时，请勿复用该命名空间。"

msgid ""
"For native streaming, `handle.namespace`, the observability `job_id`, and"
" the `RuntimeContext.job_id` are the same namespace string. The display "
"`job_name` is not a unique runtime ID. Batch and compile-only handles "
"have no Ray namespace."
msgstr ""
"对于原生流处理，`handle.namespace`、可观测性中的 `job_id` 和 `RuntimeContext.job_id` "
"是同一个命名空间字符串。显示用的 `job_name` 不是唯一运行时 ID。批处理句柄和仅编译句柄没有 Ray 命名空间。"

msgid ""
"Record `job_name`, namespace, code/configuration version, source "
"identity, and checkpoint root in deployment metadata. The namespace is "
"what `ray-klein status`, `attach`, and `cancel` use after the original "
"driver exits. See [observability](observability.md)."
msgstr ""
"请在部署元数据中记录 `job_name`、命名空间、代码/配置版本、源身份和检查点根目录。原始驱动程序退出后，`ray-klein "
"status`、`attach` 和 `cancel` 使用的是命名空间。请参阅[可观测性](observability.md)。"

msgid "Execute multiple sinks as one graph"
msgstr "将多个接收器作为一个图执行"

msgid ""
"Register every terminal before the final call when branches must share "
"upstream work and one job lifecycle:"
msgstr "当多个分支必须共享上游工作和同一个作业生命周期时，请在最终调用前注册每个终端："

msgid ""
"In batch mode, a shared fan-out may materialize the common `Dataset` so "
"its branches can reuse it. Multi-sink jobs are intended for side effects "
"and should be observed with `wait()`, not treated as an ordered aggregate"
" result."
msgstr ""
"在批处理模式下，共享的扇出可能会物化公共 `Dataset`，以便各分支复用。多接收器作业用于产生副作用，应通过 `wait()` "
"观察，而不应将其视为有序的聚合结果。"

msgid ""
"In native streaming, the job reaches `FINISHED` only after all task and "
"sink vertices finish. One job lifecycle does not imply that unrelated "
"sinks have the same external guarantee: each connector still defines its "
"own acknowledgement, idempotency, and transaction boundary. Disconnected "
"graph components can also have separate checkpoint domains. Review "
"[delivery and consistency guarantees](delivery-semantics.md) for every "
"branch."
msgstr ""
"在原生流处理中，只有所有任务和接收器顶点均完成后，作业才会进入 "
"`FINISHED`。同一个作业生命周期并不表示不相关的接收器具有相同的外部保证：每个连接器仍定义自己的确认、幂等性和事务边界。互不连接的图组件也可以拥有独立的检查点域。请为每个分支审阅[交付与一致性保证"
"](delivery-semantics.md)。"

msgid "Advanced: selective execution"
msgstr "高级：选择性执行"

msgid ""
"If one pipeline deliberately stages terminals for different submissions, "
"select explicit roots for each job. Unselected terminals remain pending:"
msgstr "如果一个管道有意为不同提交暂存多个终端，请为每个作业选择显式根。未选中的终端会保持待处理状态："

msgid ""
"An isolated context exposes the equivalent advanced form as `ctx.execute"
"(\"orders-preview\", sinks=(preview_sink,))`. Keep explicit root "
"selection local to code that genuinely needs multiple submission "
"boundaries; the normal multi-sink path is to register all terminals and "
"execute once."
msgstr ""
"隔离上下文提供等价的高级形式：`ctx.execute(\"orders-preview\", "
"sinks=(preview_sink,))`。请只在确实需要多个提交边界的代码局部使用显式根选择；常规多接收器路径是注册所有终端并执行一次。"

msgid "Cancel and drain safely"
msgstr "安全取消与排空"

msgid ""
"`handle.cancel(timeout=seconds)` serializes with recovery and operator-"
"rescale operations. A successful live cancellation:"
msgstr "`handle.cancel(timeout=seconds)` 会与恢复及算子伸缩操作串行执行。成功取消实时作业时会："

msgid "stops supervision and requests worker teardown;"
msgstr "停止监督并请求拆除工作节点；"

msgid "attempts graceful worker stop, then force-kills survivors;"
msgstr "尝试优雅停止工作节点，然后强制终止仍存活的节点；"

msgid "releases the job placement group;"
msgstr "释放作业放置组；"

msgid ""
"makes a best-effort terminal checkpoint-progress flush and stops the "
"checkpoint coordinator; and"
msgstr "尽力刷新终态检查点进度并停止检查点协调器；以及"

msgid "records `CANCELLED` and wakes waiters."
msgstr "记录 `CANCELLED` 并唤醒等待者。"

msgid ""
"The method returns `False` if the job is already terminal or if it cannot"
" acquire and finish the lifecycle operation within the timeout. A `False`"
" result does not prove that every actor has stopped; inspect the job "
"snapshot and retry through normal operational controls if necessary."
msgstr ""
"如果作业已处于终态，或者无法在超时期限内获取并完成生命周期操作，该方法会返回 `False`。`False` 并不能证明每个 actor "
"都已停止；请检查作业快照，并在必要时通过常规运维控制重试。"

msgid ""
"Cancellation is an abort, not a savepoint operation. In-flight "
"transactional sink work can be aborted, and the terminal metadata flush "
"is best effort. When you need a reproducible restore boundary, use the "
"documented checkpoint/savepoint workflow before replacing the deployment."
msgstr "取消属于中止，而不是保存点操作。进行中的事务型接收器工作可能被中止，终态元数据刷新也只是尽力而为。需要可复现的恢复边界时，请在替换部署前使用文档所述的检查点/保存点流程。"

msgid "Understand failure boundaries"
msgstr "了解故障边界"

msgid "Worker or coordinator failure"
msgstr "工作节点或协调器故障"

msgid ""
"The `JobManager` supervises tasks and the checkpoint coordinator. "
"Recovery can replace an individual task when retained upstream data "
"permits it, or restart the wider job from the latest checkpoint. The "
"fixed-delay restart policy limits restarts within a time window; "
"exhausting that policy tears down the job and sets `FAILED`."
msgstr ""
"`JobManager` "
"监督任务和检查点协调器。当保留的上游数据允许时，恢复可以替换单个任务，也可以从最新检查点重启范围更大的作业。固定延迟重启策略限制一个时间窗口内的重启次数；耗尽该策略会拆除作业并将其设为"
" `FAILED`。"

msgid ""
"Recovery can replay records and external effects. Checkpointed managed "
"state is restored consistently with source progress, but end-to-end "
"delivery is still limited by the selected sink. See [checkpoint recovery"
"](checkpoint-recovery.md) and [delivery semantics](delivery-"
"semantics.md)."
msgstr ""
"恢复可能重放记录和外部副作用。检查点中的托管状态会与源进度一致地恢复，但端到端交付仍受所选接收器限制。请参阅[检查点恢复](checkpoint-"
"recovery.md)和[交付语义](delivery-semantics.md)。"

msgid "Driver failure"
msgstr "驱动程序故障"

msgid ""
"The native streaming `JobManager` is a named, detached Ray actor. The "
"process that called `execute()` may exit or crash without cancelling the "
"dataflow. Connect another driver to the same cluster and use the recorded"
" namespace to inspect or cancel it. This does not apply when the first "
"driver is inside `handle.wait()` and receives an interrupt, because "
"`wait()` deliberately tries to cancel."
msgstr ""
"原生流处理 `JobManager` 是一个具名的分离式 Ray actor。调用 `execute()` "
"的进程可以退出或崩溃，而不取消数据流。请将另一个驱动程序连接到同一集群，并使用已记录的命名空间检查或取消作业。如果第一个驱动程序正在 "
"`handle.wait()` 内并收到中断，则不适用上述行为，因为 `wait()` 会主动尝试取消。"

msgid "JobManager failure"
msgstr "JobManager 故障"

msgid ""
"Ray is configured to restart the `JobManager` actor and retry its actor "
"tasks. However, a newly constructed manager cannot currently reconstruct "
"an already submitted logical graph from durable storage. Actual loss of "
"the JobManager process therefore requires resubmitting the same graph "
"from a durable checkpoint, despite the actor restart policy. Read [driver"
" fault tolerance](driver-fault-tolerance.md) before relying on detached "
"execution."
msgstr ""
"Ray 被配置为重启 `JobManager` actor 并重试其 actor "
"任务。但是，新构造的管理器目前无法从持久存储重建已提交的逻辑图。因此，尽管存在 actor 重启策略，一旦 JobManager "
"进程实际丢失，仍需要从持久检查点重新提交同一个图。在依赖分离式执行之前，请阅读[驱动程序容错](driver-fault-"
"tolerance.md)。"

msgid "Cluster or head/GCS failure"
msgstr "集群或 head/GCS 故障"

msgid ""
"A namespace, detached actor, and Ray Object Store data live only with the"
" Ray cluster. Losing the head/GCS service or the entire cluster loses "
"that live control plane. Start a new cluster and resubmit the compatible "
"graph with the exact completed checkpoint configured through "
"`execution.savepoint.path`. Checkpoint storage must be reachable from the"
" new cluster; local object-store state is not a durable recovery "
"boundary."
msgstr ""
"命名空间、分离式 actor 和 Ray 对象存储数据仅随 Ray 集群存在。丢失 head/GCS "
"服务或整个集群就会丢失该实时控制平面。请启动新集群，并通过 `execution.savepoint.path` "
"配置准确的已完成检查点，重新提交兼容图。新集群必须能够访问检查点存储；本地对象存储状态不是持久恢复边界。"

msgid "Persist and apply resource plans"
msgstr "持久化并应用资源计划"

msgid "`explain()` returns a JSON resource plan with:"
msgstr "`explain()` 返回包含以下内容的 JSON 资源计划："

msgid ""
"`nodes`: `id`, `name`, `num_cpus`, `num_gpus`, `concurrency`, "
"`batch_size`, and `async_buffer_size` for each logical node;"
msgstr ""
"`nodes`：每个逻辑节点的 "
"`id`、`name`、`num_cpus`、`num_gpus`、`concurrency`、`batch_size` 和 "
"`async_buffer_size`；"

msgid "`edges`: source ID, target ID, and partition strategy."
msgstr "`edges`：源 ID、目标 ID 和分区策略。"

msgid "Persist a plan while compiling an application:"
msgstr "编译应用程序时持久化计划："

msgid "Edit only the tunable node fields, then load it for a real submission:"
msgstr "仅编辑可调优的节点字段，然后在实际提交时加载该计划："

msgid ""
"A loaded plan can override only `num_cpus`, `num_gpus`, `concurrency`, "
"`batch_size`, and `async_buffer_size`. Compatibility requires the same "
"node keys, which combine operator name and numeric ID. Keep explicit "
"operator names and graph construction order stable. Serialized edges are "
"descriptive; loading a plan does not rewrite application topology or "
"partitioning."
msgstr ""
"加载的计划只能覆盖 `num_cpus`、`num_gpus`、`concurrency`、`batch_size` 和 "
"`async_buffer_size`。兼容性要求节点键相同，而节点键由算子名称和数字 ID "
"组合而成。请保持显式算子名称和图构建顺序稳定。序列化边仅用于描述；加载计划不会重写应用拓扑或分区。"

msgid ""
"Both `explain()` and `execute()` honor the load and persist variables "
"because they act during logical graph construction. A plan can therefore "
"change the JSON returned by `explain()`."
msgstr ""
"`explain()` 和 `execute()` 都会遵循加载及持久化变量，因为这些变量在逻辑图构建期间生效。因此，计划可以改变 "
"`explain()` 返回的 JSON。"

msgid "Compile-only is not a successful data run"
msgstr "仅编译不代表数据运行成功"

msgid ""
"`RAY_KLEIN_COMPILE_ONLY` is enabled by the variable's **presence**, "
"regardless of its value. In that mode Klein builds the graph, skips Ray "
"initialization and all actors, sources, records, UDFs, and sink effects, "
"and returns a completed handle whose `get()` value is the logical graph."
msgstr ""
"只要变量**存在**，无论其值为何，都会启用 `RAY_KLEIN_COMPILE_ONLY`。在该模式下，Klein 构建图，跳过 Ray "
"初始化以及所有 actor、源、记录、UDF 和接收器副作用，并返回一个完成句柄，其 `get()` 值为逻辑图。"

msgid ""
"Its `status` is `FINISHED` because compilation finished, not because the "
"data job ran. This distinction matters in automation: never treat a "
"compile-only handle as delivery evidence."
msgstr "其 `status` 为 `FINISHED`，是因为编译完成，而不是数据作业已经运行。这个区别对自动化非常重要：绝不要把仅编译句柄当成交付证据。"

msgid "Unset all three workflow variables after use:"
msgstr "使用后请取消设置全部三个工作流变量："

msgid ""
"Otherwise a later invocation can silently compile without executing, load"
" an old tuning plan, or overwrite a plan artifact."
msgstr "否则，后续调用可能在不执行的情况下静默编译、加载旧调优计划，或覆盖计划产物。"

msgid "Cleanup checklist"
msgstr "清理检查清单"

msgid ""
"Normal finish, successful cancellation, and permanent failure tear down "
"stream workers, stop the coordinator, and release the placement group. "
"Forced cleanup kills workers that did not stop gracefully. Cleanup does "
"**not** undo external sink writes or delete durable checkpoint files."
msgstr "正常完成、成功取消和永久失败都会拆除流处理工作节点、停止协调器并释放放置组。强制清理会终止未能优雅停止的工作节点。清理**不会**撤销外部接收器写入，也不会删除持久检查点文件。"

msgid "After a job ends:"
msgstr "作业结束后："

msgid ""
"Confirm the terminal status and capture failure details or the last "
"completed checkpoint before disposing of deployment metadata."
msgstr "在丢弃部署元数据之前，确认终态，并保存故障详情或最后一个已完成的检查点。"

msgid ""
"Confirm no active job remains before reusing an explicit namespace. A "
"terminal detached `JobManager` can remain addressable, and the cluster-"
"wide state actor retains a bounded in-memory terminal history. `ray-klein"
" list` hides terminal entries by default; use `ray-klein list --all` to "
"inspect them."
msgstr ""
"复用显式命名空间之前，请确认没有活动作业残留。处于终态的分离式 `JobManager` 仍可能可寻址，集群范围的状态 actor "
"也会保留有界的内存终态历史。`ray-klein list` 默认隐藏终态条目；请使用 `ray-klein list --all` 检查它们。"

msgid ""
"Apply the application's checkpoint-retention policy separately. "
"Cancellation does not erase checkpoints, staging artifacts governed by a "
"connector, or committed external data."
msgstr "请单独应用应用程序的检查点保留策略。取消不会擦除检查点、由连接器管理的暂存产物或已提交的外部数据。"

msgid ""
"Select sinks explicitly for each submission. Successful submission "
"consumes those pending sink registrations. If using the advanced isolated"
" API, discard its `KleinContext` when finished; it has no runtime "
"`close()` method."
msgstr ""
"为每次提交明确确定接收器。提交成功后会消费这些待处理的接收器注册。如果使用高级隔离 API，请在完成后丢弃其 "
"`KleinContext`；它没有运行时 `close()` 方法。"

msgid ""
"Unset compile-only and resource-plan environment variables used by build "
"or deployment tooling."
msgstr "取消设置构建或部署工具使用的仅编译和资源计划环境变量。"

msgid ""
"There is no public terminal-job purge operation. Use unique automatic "
"namespaces for routine submissions, and manage cluster lifetime through "
"the Ray deployment rather than calling internal actor-kill helpers."
msgstr "目前没有公共的终态作业清除操作。常规提交请使用唯一的自动命名空间，并通过 Ray 部署管理集群生命周期，而不要调用内部 actor 终止辅助函数。"

msgid ""
"For production procedures, continue with [deployment](deployment.md), "
"[observability](observability.md), [checkpoint recovery](checkpoint-"
"recovery.md), and [troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关生产流程，请继续阅读[部署](deployment.md)、[可观测性](observability.md)、[检查点恢复"
"](checkpoint-recovery.md)和[故障排除](troubleshooting.md)。"

